effect.name: TAP Fractal Doubler
effect.description:
TAP Fractal Doubler (LADSPA 2156)
Suitable for doubling tracks with vocals, acoustic/electric guitars, bass and just about any other instrument on them.
effect.author: http://www.ladspa.org

parameter.name: Time Tracking
parameter.comment:
Determines how "rough" and how big
these changes are. When set to 0, changes are bigger and more chaotic ("bad backup singer"). When set to 1, changes are smaller and smoother ("better tracking of the original").

parameter.name: Pitch Tracking
parameter.comment:
Determines how "rough" and how big
these changes are. When set to 0, changes are bigger and more chaotic ("bad backup singer"). When set to 1, changes are smaller and smoother ("better tracking of the original").

parameter.name: Dry Left Position
parameter.comment:
These controls range between 0 and 1,
0 meaning hard left and 1 meaning hard right position.

parameter.name: Dry Right Position
parameter.comment:
These controls range between 0 and 1,
0 meaning hard left and 1 meaning hard right position.

parameter.name: Wet Left Position
parameter.comment:
These controls range between 0 and 1,
0 meaning hard left and 1 meaning hard right position.

parameter.name: Wet Right Position
parameter.comment:
These controls range between 0 and 1,
0 meaning hard left and 1 meaning hard right position.
